  "texts": [
    "Regarding task recommendations, E1 seeks more targeted suggestions that adhere closely to instructions without becoming too divergent.",
    "In contrast, E3 emphasizes that approaching goals from different perspectives can yield valuable insights and strategies in their work scenarios.",
    "These differing viewpoints highlight the need for the planning algorithm to be adaptable to user preferences.",
    "This section outlines the limitations of our work and discuss the implications learned from the research with the future directions.Generalizability of the framework: Our framework is generalizable in two aspects.",
    "First, our conceptual framework unifies the development and usage of VA systems, based on the connections between goals, tasks, visualizations, and insights."
  ]
